=== 2014年重建至今 ===
[[2014年克里米亞危机|2014年克里米亞危机]]中由于乌克兰政府军瘫痪无力应对危局，[[乌克兰最高拉达|乌克兰最高拉达]]于3月11日提出并于3月12日通过第4393号法令《关于乌克兰国民警卫队》而重建了乌克兰国民警卫队<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.rbc.ua/rus/news/politics/rada-sozdala-natsionalnuyu-gvardiyu-ukrainy-13032014114500 |trans-title = Rada of Ukraine created the National Guard (English translation of title) |website = rbc.ua |date = 13 March 2014 |language = uk |accessdate = 2015-01-25 |archive-date = 2014-09-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140924041123/http://www.rbc.ua/rus/news/politics/rada-sozdala-natsionalnuyu-gvardiyu-ukrainy-13032014114500 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://w1.c1.rada.gov.ua/pls/zweb2/webproc4_1?pf3511=50122 Draft Law of Ukraine on the National Guard] {{Wayback|url=http://w1.c1.rada.gov.ua/pls/zweb2/webproc4_1?pf3511=50122 |date=20140607091627 }} [English translation of title]. [[乌克兰最高拉达|乌克兰最高拉达]] 官网 {{in lang|uk}}.</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.nr2.ru/kiev/488427.html|trans-title=In Ukraine, announced the creation of the National Guard begins mobilization experienced military (English translation of title) |website=www.NR2.ru |date=11 March 2014|dead-url=yes |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311164430/http://www.nr2.ru/kiev/488427.html |archivedate=2014年3月11日 |language=ru |access-date=2015年1月25日}}</ref>，员额33000人，担负保持公共秩序、保护重要地点如核电站、保卫宪法秩序、恢复国家机构的活动等任务<ref name="globalsec">[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/ukraine/ng.htm GlobalSecurity.org entry on the Ukrainian National Guard] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/ukraine/ng.htm |date=20210824140506 }}, accessed 24th March, 2014.</ref>。组建的乌克兰国民警卫队以各右翼党派的民兵武装为基础<ref name="dw">{{cite news |url=http://www.dw.de/can-the-national-guard-save-ukraine/a-17511315 |title=Can the National Guard save Ukraine? |publisher=[[德国之声|德国之声]] |date=20 March 2014 |accessdate=2015-01-25 |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428002527/http://www.dw.de/can-the-national-guard-save-ukraine/a-17511315 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随着对东乌克兰的内战的进行，也直接招募兵员<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26558288|title=Ukraine creates National Guard ahead of Crimea vote|website=BBC.com|date=13 March 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2021-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025034546/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26558288|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月16日，亚采纽克政府宣布在半个月内为乌克兰国民警卫队招募1万兵员。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26605862|title=Kiev expects West response after Crimea vote|website=BBC.com|date=16 March 2014|accessdate=2015-01-25|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102175852/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-26605862|dead-url=no}}</ref>也接纳个人志愿者投靠入伍。

为应对当时的克里米亚局势，乌克兰国民警卫队担负了第109号法令（《{{tsl|en|Criminal Code of Ukraine|乌克兰刑法}}》）规定的打击“意图暴力颠覆、改变宪法秩序、夺取国家权力的活动” {{NoteTag|"Actions aimed at the violent overthrow, change of constitutional order, or the seizure of state power"}}，执行{{tsl|en|Counter-insurgency|反叛乱}}、镇压[[第五纵队|第五纵队]]、反[[渗透|渗透]]。

乌克兰国民警卫队从最高拉达批准的紧急预算中获得了大约6亿美元的经费，用于采购装备、修理维护、训练招募<ref>{{cite news |last=Faiola|first=Anthony|title = Ukraine mobilizes reservists but relies on diplomacy |url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/ukraine-activates-reserves-pledges-military-build-up-after-crimea-vote/2014/03/17/aa707502-adc1-11e3-96dc-d6ea14c099f9_story.html |access-date=24 March 2014|newspaper=Washington Post|date=17 March 2014|archive-date=2014-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319095822/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/ukraine-activates-reserves-pledges-military-build-up-after-crimea-vote/2014/03/17/aa707502-adc1-11e3-96dc-d6ea14c099f9_story.html |dead-url=no}}</ref>。本来期望乌克兰国民警卫队达到60000人的规模。乌克兰国民警卫队的人均月薪为214欧元（297美元），与乌克兰社会平均月薪相当；军官的平均月薪两倍于此。<ref name="dw" />.内务部队的部分人员担负了对民族卫队的后勤保障与训练任务。

== 现行编制 ==
* 总部 
* 若干地区指挥部
